jumpingalien.model

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • jumpingalien.model.GameObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Creature, Plant, Spider

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds a couple of rectangles with the origin at the bottom-left that tells where the Game Object is located (the whole rectangle and its left-, right-, up- and down-border), images to show the animation of the Game Object and one of them is used to display the current pose; a world where the Game Object can be attached to that will handle the collision with other Game Objects
    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    Seppe Lesschaeve (Informatica)
    Invariant:
    ...
        hasProperWorld()
